<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="repay-vt">repay <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'peɪ/    美 /rɪ'peɪ/  </p>
<p>(repaid, repaid)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>归还；偿还；报答：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He promised to repay me the money in a week. 
他承诺一周内还我钱。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hard work that you do now will be repaid later in life. 
你现在所做的艰苦工作将在以后的生活中获得回报。</p><footer>2012 湖南</footer></div></div>